name: - I Did Something Really Extraordinary Today -
description: In a Solo Exhibition, the work should be granted an individual room. All faces of the room must be painted white. In a group Show, the work may be exhibited on a continuous stretch of white wall spanning 4 meters long. The paint will be smooth and continuous, with no form of artifice present. This NFT gives you the rights to exhibit the work, physical or virtual. @isaiahcheng_
